WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 8=

00:01:24.690 --> 00:01:27.770
♪I want to look at you, hold you close♪

00:01:28.020 --> 00:01:31.740
♪I want to be with you every moment♪

00:01:31.740 --> 00:01:35.260
♪No matter how wide the world is♪

00:01:35.260 --> 00:01:38.540
♪I'll always stay devoted to you♪

00:01:38.540 --> 00:01:42.050
♪Always thinking of you, loving you true♪

00:01:42.050 --> 00:01:45.540
♪Always meeting you in my dreams♪

00:01:45.540 --> 00:01:48.850
♪Falling for this sweet feeling♪

00:01:48.850 --> 00:01:50.820
♪Starting today♪

00:01:50.820 --> 00:01:57.100
♪You're the one and only for me♪

00:01:59.380 --> 00:02:00.260
Thanks.

00:02:00.260 --> 00:02:01.690
Not bad.

00:02:02.930 --> 00:02:04.540
Didn't expect you to sing that well.

00:02:04.900 --> 00:02:06.330
He always picks this song.

00:02:06.740 --> 00:02:07.580
Are you her fan?

00:02:07.740 --> 00:02:08.890
Not exactly.

00:02:08.890 --> 00:02:10.100
My girlfriend's a big fan.

00:02:10.450 --> 00:02:11.290
Well…

00:02:11.540 --> 00:02:12.660
My show's done.

00:02:12.940 --> 00:02:14.630
Hey, your turn... keep singing.

00:02:14.770 --> 00:02:16.090
I think I'll skip singing.

00:02:16.220 --> 00:02:17.140
Bei.

00:02:17.150 --> 00:02:18.130
Come on, Bei, your turn.

00:02:21.010 --> 00:02:22.410
Or we could sing one together.

00:02:22.900 --> 00:02:23.820
What should we sing?

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:25.610
Let's see, what should we sing?

00:02:27.100 --> 00:02:29.170
I don't know many songs. Take a look.

00:02:29.540 --> 00:02:30.500
What do you wanna sing?

00:02:34.690 --> 00:02:35.530
How about this one?

00:02:36.540 --> 00:02:37.850
Isn't this too high?

00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.260
Can you handle that?

00:02:40.410 --> 00:02:41.730
That's enough.

00:02:41.850 --> 00:02:44.220
Come on. It's just picking a song.

00:02:44.500 --> 00:02:46.100
Duets are always hard to choose.

00:02:46.100 --> 00:02:47.380
Either I don't know it,

00:02:47.380 --> 00:02:48.820
or it's way too high.

00:02:49.780 --> 00:02:51.410
You're always busy making money.

00:02:51.410 --> 00:02:53.170
Don't you even listen to music?

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:54.250
I'll pick one for you.

00:02:54.500 --> 00:02:55.940
- No need.
- You're welcome.

00:02:55.940 --> 00:02:56.780
Hey.

00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:00.940
You two are way too lovey-dovey.

00:03:01.620 --> 00:03:02.940
This song's perfect for you.

00:03:03.180 --> 00:03:04.420
Warp and Weft.

00:03:04.820 --> 00:03:08.620
(Warp and Weft; Lyrics: Zhang Zhang/
Shiqi/Fang Hai Music: Zhang Zhang)

00:03:09.100 --> 00:03:10.140
Do you know how to sing it?

00:03:10.900 --> 00:03:11.740
Yeah, I do.

00:03:12.100 --> 00:03:13.660
- Then this one it is.
- Let's sing it.

00:03:13.670 --> 00:03:14.730
Sure.

00:03:16.600 --> 00:03:17.490
Come on.

00:03:19.050 --> 00:03:20.060
Are you out of your mind?

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:21.780
What's wrong?

00:03:22.420 --> 00:03:23.540
Why'd you pick this song?

00:03:24.290 --> 00:03:25.180
What's wrong with it?

00:03:25.180 --> 00:03:26.300
He said he knows it.

00:03:27.140 --> 00:03:28.100
What?

00:03:28.100 --> 00:03:29.690
♪Woven above the clouds♪

00:03:29.690 --> 00:03:33.550
♪Each in its destined place♪

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:36.500
♪No way to explain♪

00:03:36.500 --> 00:03:40.760
♪Those moments of unguarded honesty♪

00:03:41.570 --> 00:03:43.330
♪Marking the spot♪

00:03:43.350 --> 00:03:46.980
♪Acting like nothing happened♪

00:03:48.790 --> 00:03:50.690
♪Day and night, just the same♪

00:03:50.980 --> 00:03:54.960
♪Recording every meet and part♪

00:03:55.570 --> 00:03:57.570
♪Thinking over and again♪

00:03:57.860 --> 00:04:03.890
♪Destined to stall at some point♪

00:04:03.890 --> 00:04:06.920
♪So many what-ifs in my head♪

00:04:06.920 --> 00:04:08.640
♪In that moment of push and pull♪

00:04:08.640 --> 00:04:11.090
♪Choosing to stay instead♪

00:04:12.010 --> 00:04:13.780
♪But every time we reconnect♪

00:04:13.780 --> 00:04:15.320
♪I make my own selfish choice♪

00:04:16.860 --> 00:04:19.740
(When will you be here?)

00:04:20.520 --> 00:04:21.540
♪After the heart stirs♪

00:04:21.540 --> 00:04:22.420
♪Which side♪

00:04:22.420 --> 00:04:25.010
♪First slips into the night♪

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:27.490
♪Waiting for someone else♪

00:04:27.490 --> 00:04:29.490
♪To light the flame just right♪

00:04:29.500 --> 00:04:30.380
Is this one good?

00:04:31.660 --> 00:04:32.660
Sure.

00:04:34.420 --> 00:04:35.260
Looks nice.

00:04:37.260 --> 00:04:38.620
Bei's singing is pretty good.

00:04:38.900 --> 00:04:40.900
Of course it is, that's because…

00:04:42.700 --> 00:04:44.540
he's got a musician friend like me.

00:04:45.140 --> 00:04:46.380
Oh please.

00:04:47.140 --> 00:04:48.700
Bei's got taste. Do you?

00:04:51.060 --> 00:04:52.540
You've been drinking all night,

00:04:52.700 --> 00:04:53.940
hardly eaten anything.

00:04:55.220 --> 00:04:56.940
They ordered that flaky buns for you.

00:04:56.940 --> 00:04:58.340
It's stuffed with oysters.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:04:59.860
Yet you're not touching it.

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:01.420
Don't let their effort

00:05:01.420 --> 00:05:02.340
go to waste.

00:05:02.690 --> 00:05:04.460
I'm good. I'm full already.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.420
Don't give something that tonic to Xiu.

00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:08.900
It won't help him.

00:05:10.520 --> 00:05:13.140
Our Xiu doesn't need it anyway.

00:05:14.060 --> 00:05:14.900
But you...

00:05:14.930 --> 00:05:15.900
You don't need it either.

00:05:16.300 --> 00:05:17.380
You're all on your own.

00:05:17.860 --> 00:05:19.100
So there's really no use for it.

00:05:20.420 --> 00:05:22.380
Ouch, that hit me hard, old lady.

00:05:22.500 --> 00:05:23.780
Who're you calling old?

00:05:24.500 --> 00:05:27.500
But I think I'm about to find someone.

00:05:28.180 --> 00:05:29.540
Last week,

00:05:29.820 --> 00:05:32.260
I ran into my junior high class rep.

00:05:32.740 --> 00:05:36.700
She was stunning, graceful, and charming.

00:05:36.940 --> 00:05:38.020
Back in the day,

00:05:38.200 --> 00:05:40.330
she was always hounding me for homework.

00:05:40.420 --> 00:05:41.580
Drove me crazy.

00:05:42.630 --> 00:05:44.400
Now, if I had a chance,

00:05:45.340 --> 00:05:48.100
I'd gladly hand in homework to her.

00:05:48.100 --> 00:05:50.950
♪First slips into the night♪

00:05:51.460 --> 00:05:53.240
♪Waiting for someone else♪

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:56.150
♪To light the flame just right♪

00:05:56.590 --> 00:05:58.260
♪The love♪

00:05:59.180 --> 00:06:01.380
(An Miu)

00:06:05.700 --> 00:06:07.260
- You okay?
- Huh?

00:06:07.260 --> 00:06:08.100
- You okay?
- Yeah.

00:06:08.420 --> 00:06:09.260
Alright.

00:06:21.010 --> 00:06:22.400
♪Those caught inside♪

00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:24.930
♪Turn into bystanders♪

00:06:24.930 --> 00:06:26.940
♪The warp and weft silently♪

00:06:29.140 --> 00:06:32.250
♪Scatter without a trace♪

00:06:32.660 --> 00:06:34.360
♪Only then we realize♪

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:37.130
♪No one can escape♪

00:06:38.330 --> 00:06:39.260
♪This♪

00:06:39.260 --> 00:06:43.650
♪Law of nature♪

00:06:47.300 --> 00:06:49.660
Amazing. You have such great chemistry.

00:06:49.660 --> 00:06:50.700
Bei really led me well.

00:06:50.700 --> 00:06:51.860
I'm not familiar with it.

00:06:51.980 --> 00:06:53.100
You sing better than me.

00:06:53.980 --> 00:06:55.620
I'm gonna hit the restroom.

00:06:55.820 --> 00:06:56.660
Alright.

00:07:13.660 --> 00:07:14.660
Whoa, hey, hey.

00:07:14.780 --> 00:07:16.860
Seriously? I was just about to sing.

00:07:19.620 --> 00:07:20.500
I'll sing with you.

00:07:20.660 --> 00:07:21.740
Hello, Guan.

00:07:22.300 --> 00:07:24.060
Sorry, I was tied up just now.

00:07:24.460 --> 00:07:25.380
I know.

00:07:25.380 --> 00:07:27.100
What, you trying to avoid me now?

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:30.740
I've never asked you for anything before.

00:07:31.780 --> 00:07:32.620
I just want to

00:07:32.900 --> 00:07:34.260
ask you one last time.

00:07:35.100 --> 00:07:37.380
Are you really not going to help me?

00:07:38.980 --> 00:07:40.260
I really can't this time.

00:07:41.300 --> 00:07:42.180
Sorry.

00:07:42.650 --> 00:07:43.500
Mm.

00:07:44.780 --> 00:07:46.580
Since that's the case,

00:07:46.650 --> 00:07:47.960
I have nothing more to say.

00:07:48.690 --> 00:07:49.780
I'm really sorry.

00:07:50.050 --> 00:07:51.470
It's at Linglong on Wukang Road.

00:07:51.470 --> 00:07:53.140
Everyone's waiting for you. Hurry up!

00:07:56.540 --> 00:07:58.460
Are you eating out?

00:07:58.850 --> 00:07:59.720
Mm.

00:08:01.460 --> 00:08:02.300
Alright, go ahead.

00:08:02.540 --> 00:08:03.380
Okay.

00:08:03.580 --> 00:08:04.460
I'll hang up now.

00:08:07.700 --> 00:08:08.940
It's at Linglong on Wukang Road.

00:08:18.140 --> 00:08:19.220
You came back?

00:08:20.660 --> 00:08:21.900
Of course I want to.

00:08:23.380 --> 00:08:24.340
Yeah, yeah, I know.

00:08:24.700 --> 00:08:26.100
After I drop her off later,

00:08:26.100 --> 00:08:26.940
I'll come find you.

00:08:28.380 --> 00:08:29.500
Alright, got it.

00:08:29.500 --> 00:08:30.580
Go take a shower first.

00:08:34.020 --> 00:08:35.820
(An Miu)

00:08:38.100 --> 00:08:40.020
Then I'll bring you
some late-night snacks.

00:08:40.780 --> 00:08:42.780
From that crayfish place you love.

00:08:47.140 --> 00:08:47.980
Mm.

00:08:48.580 --> 00:08:50.380
Fine. Talk when I get there.

00:08:50.380 --> 00:08:51.620
Just wait till we meet, alright?

00:08:52.740 --> 00:08:53.580
Bye.

00:08:53.740 --> 00:08:54.580
Bye.

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:17.460
What's wrong with you?

00:09:20.500 --> 00:09:21.500
Let's break up.

00:09:23.780 --> 00:09:24.860
Why?

00:09:25.780 --> 00:09:26.900
Did I do something wrong?

00:09:28.300 --> 00:09:30.180
Don't you know what you did?

00:09:31.620 --> 00:09:33.820
I don't know what you're talking about.
What's going on?

00:09:34.060 --> 00:09:34.980
Quit pretending.

00:09:37.740 --> 00:09:39.540
Do you want me to say her name?

00:09:55.500 --> 00:09:56.420
You mean...

00:09:58.540 --> 00:09:59.540
Su Yunyi, right?

00:10:03.060 --> 00:10:03.900
How long has it been?

00:10:09.940 --> 00:10:11.060
Since college.

00:10:12.460 --> 00:10:13.420
Back at that time,

00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:15.860
she became my...

00:10:18.340 --> 00:10:19.220
instructor.

00:10:27.580 --> 00:10:28.980
That's kind of mean of you, huh?

00:10:28.980 --> 00:10:30.460
You even dragged Ms. Su into this.

00:10:30.940 --> 00:10:32.300
You guys, seriously.

00:10:32.420 --> 00:10:34.220
Having fun with the King's Game, huh?

00:10:34.500 --> 00:10:35.500
You knew?

00:10:35.700 --> 00:10:36.940
- Yeah.
- I had no choice.

00:10:36.940 --> 00:10:38.500
They made me say, "Let's break up."

00:10:38.500 --> 00:10:39.340
They're too evil.

00:10:39.340 --> 00:10:40.700
Your eyes are turning red.

00:10:40.820 --> 00:10:42.700
Wow, your acting's way too real.

00:10:43.060 --> 00:10:46.020
I thought we'd dig up some gossip.

00:10:46.020 --> 00:10:47.100
What a letdown.

00:10:47.100 --> 00:10:47.940
They're so mean.

00:10:48.140 --> 00:10:50.020
Stop messing with my girlfriend.

00:10:50.020 --> 00:10:51.860
Alright, enough with the sweet talk.

00:10:51.860 --> 00:10:53.420
Come on, are we playing or not?

00:10:53.620 --> 00:10:54.460
- Let's go.
- Yeah.

00:10:58.460 --> 00:11:00.020
Hey, I'm the King.

00:11:00.040 --> 00:11:00.980
Ah.

00:11:00.980 --> 00:11:01.860
Come on.

00:11:02.620 --> 00:11:03.540
I don't need to say it.

00:11:03.540 --> 00:11:04.900
You all know what I'm about to ask.

00:11:05.540 --> 00:11:08.860
Your first sex in your relationship?

00:11:09.940 --> 00:11:11.900
Let's ask Number 2 then.

00:11:15.700 --> 00:11:16.580
Number 2.

00:11:18.060 --> 00:11:19.060
Who's Number 2?

00:11:19.060 --> 00:11:20.100
Number 2.

00:11:29.860 --> 00:11:30.740
Soon.

00:11:33.180 --> 00:11:34.420
Do you even have a clue?

00:11:34.420 --> 00:11:35.620
Last time you said it was 18.

00:11:35.980 --> 00:11:37.940
Why do I always get this question?

00:11:39.260 --> 00:11:40.260
Cards down. Cards down.

00:11:47.740 --> 00:11:49.060
I drew the King.

00:11:49.180 --> 00:11:50.980
Wow.

00:11:51.860 --> 00:11:53.220
I can order a few people, right?

00:11:53.580 --> 00:11:54.420
Of course.

00:11:55.900 --> 00:11:57.020
Then...

00:11:57.300 --> 00:11:58.380
Number 1 picks a song.

00:11:58.660 --> 00:11:59.820
Number 2 and 3 sing it.

00:12:00.180 --> 00:12:01.540
Number 1, that's me.

00:12:02.420 --> 00:12:03.780
Close to Love.

00:12:04.060 --> 00:12:04.980
Numbers 2 and 3, sing.

00:12:06.260 --> 00:12:07.180
I'm Number 3.

00:12:09.140 --> 00:12:14.660
♪I heard you and I share the same feeling♪

00:12:23.980 --> 00:12:28.620
♪Maybe it's that sweet, heartfelt magic♪

00:12:32.780 --> 00:12:33.980
So you're messing with us?

00:12:34.380 --> 00:12:35.300
What lame song is that?

00:12:35.300 --> 00:12:36.980
You seemed pretty into it.

00:12:37.220 --> 00:12:39.260
I take singing seriously.

00:12:39.260 --> 00:12:41.300
But singing with this punk? Total waste.

00:12:41.300 --> 00:12:42.320
Who'd wanna sing with you?

00:12:42.580 --> 00:12:43.420
Ugh.

00:12:43.500 --> 00:12:44.340
Hey.

00:12:44.340 --> 00:12:45.180
How about...

00:12:47.220 --> 00:12:48.100
we sing together?

00:12:48.460 --> 00:12:49.460
I'm not singing with you.

00:12:49.740 --> 00:12:51.340
Come on, I've already picked the song.

00:12:52.100 --> 00:12:52.940
Total waste.

00:12:53.980 --> 00:12:58.700
♪I don't care if I'll ever get the chance♪

00:12:59.900 --> 00:13:05.060
♪I still have the courage to keep going♪

00:13:05.500 --> 00:13:09.780
♪Even if I'm down and need someone by my side♪

00:13:10.180 --> 00:13:14.540
(Mingming)
♪In the end, it all fades into tiredness♪

00:13:14.540 --> 00:13:15.580
(Sen, I'm sorry.)

00:13:15.580 --> 00:13:17.580
(I'm not feeling great tonight,)

00:13:17.780 --> 00:13:18.860
(so I'm not coming.)

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.460
(I'll hang out at my friend's place.)

00:13:20.660 --> 00:13:21.820
(Let's talk later, okay?)

00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:23.100
(Have fun out there.)

00:13:23.700 --> 00:13:25.660
Nice singing. Let's do the next round.

00:13:38.380 --> 00:13:39.380
I'm the King.

00:13:40.700 --> 00:13:41.780
Ask Number 3.

00:13:43.020 --> 00:13:44.820
Well… Would you mind

00:13:44.820 --> 00:13:45.900
if your partner had

00:13:46.300 --> 00:13:47.940
a really close friend of the opposite sex?

00:13:48.900 --> 00:13:50.180
Like a...

00:13:50.620 --> 00:13:52.740
you know, that kind of close confidant.

00:14:02.100 --> 00:14:02.940
Number 3.

00:14:02.940 --> 00:14:03.780
Well,

00:14:04.660 --> 00:14:06.180
I think everyone's free.

00:14:06.180 --> 00:14:07.980
Who they're friends with is their choice.

00:14:08.420 --> 00:14:09.500
I shouldn't interfere.

00:14:11.460 --> 00:14:13.540
Even if they hang out alone?

00:14:13.900 --> 00:14:15.700
Like dinner or shopping together.

00:14:15.700 --> 00:14:16.680
That wouldn't bother you?

00:14:17.300 --> 00:14:18.460
I think...

00:14:19.160 --> 00:14:20.020
my girlfriend

00:14:20.020 --> 00:14:21.340
wouldn't put me in that situation.

00:14:23.860 --> 00:14:25.500
So what you're really saying is...

00:14:35.540 --> 00:14:37.540
The truth is,

00:14:39.580 --> 00:14:41.060
freedom is right there,

00:14:42.540 --> 00:14:44.060
but you'd better not push your luck.

00:14:45.100 --> 00:14:46.300
I'm not that possessive.

00:14:47.180 --> 00:14:49.660
If Xiaoxi has some great male friends,

00:14:51.020 --> 00:14:52.100
I'd love to meet them too.

00:14:52.580 --> 00:14:53.860
Well, that's a coincidence.

00:14:56.180 --> 00:14:58.220
Let's get to know each other then.

00:15:08.060 --> 00:15:08.940
Sorry,

00:15:09.660 --> 00:15:10.660
except for the thugs.

00:15:11.460 --> 00:15:13.060
Alright, let's keep going.

00:15:13.060 --> 00:15:16.180
Do you think love can make you better?

00:15:16.460 --> 00:15:18.380
Like stronger and more independent?

00:15:18.940 --> 00:15:20.540
Would that count as being better?

00:15:21.220 --> 00:15:23.620
If life could start over,

00:15:24.420 --> 00:15:26.460
would you still choose each other?

00:15:26.900 --> 00:15:28.340
He deserves someone better.

00:15:29.500 --> 00:15:30.460
Me too.

00:15:31.020 --> 00:15:33.420
What makes you happiest?

00:15:37.260 --> 00:15:38.140
You.

00:15:39.940 --> 00:15:43.700
What's the best state of love?

00:15:44.020 --> 00:15:44.900
Loving each other.

00:15:44.900 --> 00:15:47.940
Or maybe not loving each other anymore.

00:15:48.340 --> 00:15:50.260
The worst thing is

00:15:51.940 --> 00:15:53.980
when love's already dead,

00:15:55.100 --> 00:15:58.820
but you're still trying a hopeless fix.

00:15:59.140 --> 00:16:00.340
What's your biggest regret?

00:16:01.140 --> 00:16:03.260
Turns out not everyone's meant for marriage.

00:16:03.780 --> 00:16:04.740
But if you never marry,

00:16:05.100 --> 00:16:06.580
how do you know you're not?

00:16:07.020 --> 00:16:08.700
Life's meant for trial and error.

00:16:09.500 --> 00:16:10.620
The sad part is,

00:16:10.860 --> 00:16:11.820
you really got it wrong.

00:16:12.220 --> 00:16:13.060
Wrong.

00:16:13.740 --> 00:16:15.820
With our limited experience and insight,

00:16:15.980 --> 00:16:16.820
how are we supposed

00:16:16.820 --> 00:16:18.340
to choose someone to spend

00:16:18.860 --> 00:16:20.420
the next few decades with?

00:16:20.860 --> 00:16:22.700
Love, breakups,

00:16:23.060 --> 00:16:24.980
marriage, divorce,

00:16:25.500 --> 00:16:27.140
all the ups and downs.

00:16:27.580 --> 00:16:29.300
Every rational choice we make...

00:16:29.620 --> 00:16:32.020
isn't it all just to live a better life?

00:16:32.460 --> 00:16:34.060
Willing to give it all.

00:16:34.820 --> 00:16:36.740
Why am I being treated like this?

00:16:37.780 --> 00:16:39.500
Love and fairness

00:16:39.900 --> 00:16:41.940
are totally two different things.

00:16:42.660 --> 00:16:43.780
Complaints like this

00:16:44.020 --> 00:16:46.580
are just refusing to face the outcome.

00:16:51.300 --> 00:16:53.580
The most unforgettable thing an ex ever did?

00:16:53.580 --> 00:16:54.540
Becoming my ex.

00:16:54.860 --> 00:16:56.020
We're really just

00:16:56.340 --> 00:16:58.700
looking for a simple, ordinary love.

00:16:59.580 --> 00:17:01.260
Why is that so hard?

00:17:03.220 --> 00:17:04.780
In the world of adults,

00:17:06.300 --> 00:17:07.180
nothing's ever simple.

00:17:07.540 --> 00:17:08.900
Chasing ordinary

00:17:09.740 --> 00:17:11.540
might just be another form of greed.

00:17:24.580 --> 00:17:25.700
What's wrong, Xiaoxi?

00:17:28.540 --> 00:17:30.700
I'm fine, maybe just a little tipsy.

00:17:31.900 --> 00:17:32.980
Here, drink my water.

00:17:33.100 --> 00:17:33.940
Drink this.

00:17:35.140 --> 00:17:36.180
I'm tipsy too.

00:17:36.920 --> 00:17:38.230
Go wash your face in the bathroom.

00:17:38.230 --> 00:17:39.090
Snap out of it.

00:17:39.090 --> 00:17:40.060
This is getting boring.

00:17:40.660 --> 00:17:42.020
Who drew the King? Hurry up.

00:17:42.500 --> 00:17:43.500
Where's the King?

00:17:43.820 --> 00:17:45.020
Speak up if you got it.

00:17:48.780 --> 00:17:50.940
Why rush? Still thinking of a challenge.

00:17:51.220 --> 00:17:52.540
If you can't think of one, ask me.

00:17:52.540 --> 00:17:54.100
I've been a master in this game.

00:17:54.580 --> 00:17:56.100
Hey, it's me! It's me!

00:17:56.100 --> 00:17:57.420
Alright. Stop it.

00:17:57.420 --> 00:17:58.660
I didn't catch that just now.

00:18:01.580 --> 00:18:03.140
Number 6. I'll ask Number 6.

00:18:03.740 --> 00:18:04.820
Yeah, that's you.

00:18:04.820 --> 00:18:06.460
If your...

00:18:06.660 --> 00:18:08.540
If your closest friend asked to

00:18:08.540 --> 00:18:09.580
borrow money from you,

00:18:10.340 --> 00:18:11.300
would you lend it?

00:18:13.300 --> 00:18:14.140
Sure.

00:18:22.180 --> 00:18:23.020
How much?

00:18:24.180 --> 00:18:25.100
Three...

00:18:25.100 --> 00:18:26.980
Three… three hundred thousand.

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:29.260
Okay. I'll transfer it tomorrow.

00:18:29.260 --> 00:18:31.540
Whoa, what's going on here?

00:18:31.700 --> 00:18:32.540
Number 6.

00:18:32.660 --> 00:18:34.020
Am I your closest buddy?

00:18:35.620 --> 00:18:36.500
Just average friends.

00:18:38.140 --> 00:18:38.980
Wait, Sen.

00:18:39.100 --> 00:18:40.660
Why suddenly ask for so much money?

00:18:41.180 --> 00:18:43.220
Just investing in something.

00:18:43.660 --> 00:18:44.900
Investing in love?

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:47.580
Be careful with that.

00:18:48.140 --> 00:18:49.740
Love doesn't have high returns.

00:18:49.740 --> 00:18:51.580
Love doesn't need returns.

00:18:51.720 --> 00:18:53.300
Right. Those girls who borrowed from you?

00:18:53.300 --> 00:18:54.340
They just left afterwards.

00:18:54.340 --> 00:18:55.660
So you didn't get any returns.

00:18:55.660 --> 00:18:56.780
You just love arguing, huh?

00:18:56.780 --> 00:18:58.380
Love built on a material foundation.

00:18:58.380 --> 00:18:59.220
That's fine.

00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:01.380
But if it's only built on material things,

00:19:01.380 --> 00:19:02.380
that's a big problem.

00:19:02.620 --> 00:19:04.540
You haven't been together long. Be careful.

00:19:04.540 --> 00:19:06.380
Oh, stop worrying about it.

00:19:06.700 --> 00:19:08.180
I'm just investing in the future.

00:19:08.580 --> 00:19:09.420
Hey.

00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:10.780
Speaking of which,

00:19:10.780 --> 00:19:12.140
why isn't your girlfriend here yet?

00:19:12.140 --> 00:19:13.540
Oh, I forgot to tell you.

00:19:14.460 --> 00:19:17.020
Something came up, so she's not coming.

00:19:17.620 --> 00:19:18.540
But it's fine.

00:19:18.550 --> 00:19:19.740
There'll be plenty of chances.

00:19:19.900 --> 00:19:22.180
I'll take you to meet her another time.

00:19:23.060 --> 00:19:24.900
Oh?

00:19:25.820 --> 00:19:27.100
What a coincidence.

00:19:32.300 --> 00:19:33.540
Sir, do you have a reservation?

00:19:33.860 --> 00:19:34.700
Sir.

00:19:41.820 --> 00:19:43.740
- Split up. You come with me.
- Hey.

00:19:43.740 --> 00:19:45.020
If you spot her, call me.

00:19:47.780 --> 00:19:48.820
Me again.

00:19:49.510 --> 00:19:50.380
Number 5.

00:19:50.380 --> 00:19:52.380
Call the last person you spoke to.

00:19:52.820 --> 00:19:53.980
Come on, it's so late.

00:19:53.980 --> 00:19:54.820
Don't make the call.

00:19:56.580 --> 00:19:57.420
Hey.

00:19:57.580 --> 00:19:58.780
If I remember right,

00:19:58.780 --> 00:20:00.620
your last call was with me, wasn't it?

00:20:00.940 --> 00:20:01.940
Why so nervous?

00:20:06.520 --> 00:20:07.380
On speaker?

00:20:07.380 --> 00:20:08.260
Of course.

00:20:19.380 --> 00:20:20.940
Fine, I'll call then.

00:20:20.940 --> 00:20:21.820
I'm Number 5.

00:20:22.420 --> 00:20:23.980
No sneaky moves.

00:20:23.980 --> 00:20:25.500
Pull up your call log.

00:20:26.020 --> 00:20:26.900
Sure thing.

00:20:29.460 --> 00:20:31.220
(An Miu)

00:20:36.220 --> 00:20:37.060
Take a shower first.

00:20:37.060 --> 00:20:38.570
I'll bring you
some late-night snacks.

00:20:39.100 --> 00:20:41.020
From that crayfish place you love.

00:20:42.460 --> 00:20:44.660
(An Miu)

00:20:45.020 --> 00:20:45.860
(An Miu?)

00:20:46.980 --> 00:20:47.820
(Is it a girl?)

00:20:48.580 --> 00:20:49.460
(Colleague?)

00:20:49.460 --> 00:20:50.300
(Friend?)

00:20:50.740 --> 00:20:51.660
(Could it be)

00:20:52.260 --> 00:20:53.100
(his ex?)

00:20:59.660 --> 00:21:00.500
Hello.

00:21:00.660 --> 00:21:03.500
The number you have dialed is unavailable.

00:21:03.780 --> 00:21:05.460
Please try again later.

00:21:07.140 --> 00:21:08.420
You're lucky.

00:21:16.740 --> 00:21:18.220
Once suspicion takes root,

00:21:18.780 --> 00:21:20.100
the blame's already there.

00:21:21.980 --> 00:21:24.220
(Then please, let me believe in you.)

00:21:30.140 --> 00:21:31.300
Happy birthday!

00:21:31.300 --> 00:21:32.140
Hey.

00:21:32.540 --> 00:21:33.420
Who's that?

00:21:37.700 --> 00:21:38.620
Li Xiaoxi.

00:21:39.180 --> 00:21:40.060
Are you insane?

00:21:40.060 --> 00:21:40.900
Sorry about that.

00:21:42.860 --> 00:21:44.740
Uh, we'll head out after this round.

00:21:45.220 --> 00:21:46.220
Got stuff early tomorrow.

00:21:46.900 --> 00:21:47.820
Last round.

00:21:48.340 --> 00:21:50.060
Then I've got a big finale request.

00:21:51.270 --> 00:21:52.740
Number 2 kisses Number 3 on the cheek.

00:21:53.460 --> 00:21:54.460
Whoa, that's a bold move.

00:21:55.180 --> 00:21:56.020
I'm Number 3.

00:22:08.020 --> 00:22:09.260
Maybe let's just skip it.

00:22:09.740 --> 00:22:10.820
Why?

00:22:11.220 --> 00:22:12.740
You didn't skip it when it was my turn.

00:22:14.460 --> 00:22:15.300
Go on, kiss.

00:22:20.660 --> 00:22:22.860
Bei's cool. He's not that petty.

00:22:23.700 --> 00:22:25.220
Say that again and I won't lend you.

00:22:27.460 --> 00:22:28.340
Number 6.

00:22:29.860 --> 00:22:30.740
Let's be clear.

00:22:32.380 --> 00:22:33.700
Gentlemen use words, not hands.

00:22:34.380 --> 00:22:35.260
It's just a game.

00:22:35.900 --> 00:22:37.060
Come on, you're my best buddy.

00:22:37.980 --> 00:22:38.820
Alright, enough.

00:22:40.060 --> 00:22:40.900
Ready?

00:23:06.100 --> 00:23:07.380
Whoa!

00:23:07.380 --> 00:23:08.580
Wow.

00:23:10.700 --> 00:23:11.580
Pfft.

00:23:13.700 --> 00:23:15.100
What's wrong with you?

00:23:15.780 --> 00:23:17.140
Seriously, what's wrong with you?

00:23:17.540 --> 00:23:18.540
What are you doing?

00:23:18.540 --> 00:23:19.860
Get up, careful, careful.

00:23:19.980 --> 00:23:21.100
Just playing a game.

00:23:23.700 --> 00:23:25.180
You're so gross.

00:23:25.380 --> 00:23:26.540
I haven't even complained yet.

00:23:27.020 --> 00:23:28.500
So dirty. Pfft, pfft, pfft.

00:23:31.820 --> 00:23:33.500
Gong, would you call that saving the day?

00:23:33.500 --> 00:23:35.020
Nah. He just wanted to piss Bei off.

00:23:35.020 --> 00:23:36.140
Finally got his chance.

00:23:36.580 --> 00:23:37.780
You'd hit me for

00:23:38.620 --> 00:23:39.460
disrespecting it.

00:23:40.260 --> 00:23:41.140
You'd hit me for

00:23:41.140 --> 00:23:42.140
respecting it too.

00:23:42.300 --> 00:23:43.780
You're just making things hard for me.

00:23:44.220 --> 00:23:46.060
Good thing Gong teased Bei instead.

00:23:46.820 --> 00:23:48.140
If he'd done that to Xiu,

00:23:48.580 --> 00:23:49.500
I'd dump him.

00:23:49.980 --> 00:23:51.820
I'd rather he kissed a girl.

00:23:54.460 --> 00:23:55.380
You sure about that?

00:23:56.620 --> 00:23:57.500
We're heading out.

00:23:57.900 --> 00:23:58.820
Let's catch up later.

00:23:59.340 --> 00:24:00.740
Xiu, pick up the dog.

00:24:01.180 --> 00:24:02.220
Bye.

00:24:02.220 --> 00:24:03.740
I need to use the restroom.

00:24:03.740 --> 00:24:04.820
- Bye.
- Good night.

00:24:06.660 --> 00:24:08.220
Bei, I sent you my account number.

00:24:08.420 --> 00:24:10.140
No rush, just transfer it tomorrow.

00:24:10.620 --> 00:24:11.780
Alright, you can head off.

00:24:11.780 --> 00:24:13.060
Cool, I'll head out too.

00:24:13.980 --> 00:24:15.180
- Bye.
- Bye.

00:24:15.580 --> 00:24:16.420
You okay?

00:24:17.180 --> 00:24:18.020
Yeah, I'm fine.

00:24:18.020 --> 00:24:19.220
Good, as long as you're fine.

00:24:20.620 --> 00:24:21.460
You two take a seat.

00:24:21.700 --> 00:24:22.740
I'm going to the bathroom.

00:24:22.740 --> 00:24:23.780
Oh.

00:24:35.140 --> 00:24:36.780
Room 806, third floor.

00:24:37.220 --> 00:24:38.380
Found her. Get over here.

00:24:40.980 --> 00:24:42.140
Why are you avoiding me?

00:24:46.980 --> 00:24:48.180
Are you talking to me?

00:24:48.340 --> 00:24:49.460
First you disappeared,

00:24:49.740 --> 00:24:51.220
now you're playing the amnesia game?

00:24:51.220 --> 00:24:52.060
Li Xiaoxi,

00:24:54.700 --> 00:24:55.900
I know you're still mad at me.

00:24:55.900 --> 00:24:57.300
But breaking up takes time.

00:24:58.220 --> 00:24:59.300
I'm single now.

00:24:59.780 --> 00:25:01.140
You left without a word. Why?

00:25:02.260 --> 00:25:03.100
Are you insane?

00:25:03.100 --> 00:25:03.980
Yeah, I'm insane!

00:25:04.220 --> 00:25:05.340
I've called you many times.

00:25:05.580 --> 00:25:06.420
You never pick up.

00:25:06.420 --> 00:25:07.460
Nor do you reply to texts.

00:25:08.060 --> 00:25:09.180
Anyway, whatever you say...

00:25:09.180 --> 00:25:10.020
Hey, let go of me.

00:25:10.020 --> 00:25:11.110
I won't let you leave again.

00:25:11.260 --> 00:25:12.900
Wherever you go, I'll follow. Move!

00:25:12.900 --> 00:25:13.740
Let go of me!

00:25:16.100 --> 00:25:18.140
Didn't you hear her? She said let go.

00:25:18.680 --> 00:25:20.380
Even being a jerk, you gotta wait your turn.

00:25:20.780 --> 00:25:21.620
Whoa.

00:25:21.620 --> 00:25:22.860
Looks like you've got a team.

00:25:23.260 --> 00:25:25.500
Listen, take your team and get lost.

00:25:25.500 --> 00:25:26.740
This girl's with me.

00:25:29.910 --> 00:25:30.780
Wait, what...

00:25:30.780 --> 00:25:32.260
Who are you guys? What's going on?

00:25:32.940 --> 00:25:33.780
What's going on?

00:25:34.780 --> 00:25:35.820
Can't you tell?

00:25:36.100 --> 00:25:37.620
They're obviously drawn to my charm.

00:25:39.180 --> 00:25:40.060
What do you want?

00:26:49.140 --> 00:26:49.980
Xiu,

00:26:51.140 --> 00:26:52.380
how long have we been together?

00:26:54.020 --> 00:26:56.060
If we count from before graduation...

00:26:56.060 --> 00:26:57.300
About ten years.

00:27:00.060 --> 00:27:03.100
I've been thinking about us back then a lot.

00:27:04.580 --> 00:27:05.620
So young.

00:27:06.660 --> 00:27:07.580
It was a good time.

00:27:14.100 --> 00:27:15.620
Let's start over. Okay?

00:27:21.500 --> 00:27:22.380
How?

00:27:22.940 --> 00:27:23.780
Chase me.

00:27:24.620 --> 00:27:26.060
Begin with confessing to me.

00:27:30.980 --> 00:27:31.820
Sis.

00:27:32.580 --> 00:27:33.420
Why'd you ask me out?

00:27:33.860 --> 00:27:34.700
This is for you.

00:27:36.380 --> 00:27:37.300
What's this?

00:27:37.940 --> 00:27:38.900
It's called a unicorn.

00:27:39.140 --> 00:27:41.100
It stands for loyalty in love.

00:27:42.740 --> 00:27:44.820
Anyway, I won't call you Sis anymore.

00:27:45.140 --> 00:27:46.540
I want to call you Yu.

00:27:46.820 --> 00:27:48.700
Or Little Yu, or Baby.

00:27:48.700 --> 00:27:49.540
Whatever works.

00:27:49.540 --> 00:27:50.380
Just never Sis again.

00:27:51.340 --> 00:27:52.580
You must be out of your mind.

00:27:55.340 --> 00:27:56.180
I like you.

00:27:56.420 --> 00:27:57.740
I want to be with you.

00:28:00.900 --> 00:28:02.580
Kid, stop messing around.

00:28:02.600 --> 00:28:03.580
I'll see you another day.

00:28:03.580 --> 00:28:04.660
I told you, no more Sis.

00:28:06.620 --> 00:28:08.740
Fine, call me whatever you want.

00:28:10.220 --> 00:28:11.060
But...

00:28:13.420 --> 00:28:14.460
Us? Not happening.

00:28:15.340 --> 00:28:16.780
You're not considering love at all?

00:28:16.780 --> 00:28:17.860
Or just not considering me?

00:28:18.700 --> 00:28:20.300
Do you feel I'm younger than you?

00:28:20.300 --> 00:28:21.260
And too naive?

00:28:21.460 --> 00:28:23.020
That I can't give you the life you want?

00:28:23.250 --> 00:28:24.140
I admit it.

00:28:24.140 --> 00:28:26.060
I'm not that mature.

00:28:26.300 --> 00:28:27.940
But I know what responsibility

00:28:27.940 --> 00:28:28.780
in love means.

00:28:29.380 --> 00:28:30.260
And

00:28:30.260 --> 00:28:32.100
I believe love lies in

00:28:32.100 --> 00:28:34.860
finding joy in the everyday trifles.

00:28:35.820 --> 00:28:37.300
Of course, that's just my take.

00:28:37.580 --> 00:28:38.900
Nothing to do with maturity.

00:28:40.220 --> 00:28:41.380
Truth is, for pursuing you,

00:28:41.380 --> 00:28:43.300
I've thought far more than you have.

00:28:47.980 --> 00:28:49.300
Have you ever thought about it?

00:28:50.260 --> 00:28:51.940
Ten years later, I'll be pushing forty.

00:28:52.460 --> 00:28:54.140
And you'll be just past thirty.

00:28:54.420 --> 00:28:56.140
Right when your career's taking off,

00:28:56.140 --> 00:28:57.620
exuding the charm of a mature man,

00:28:57.620 --> 00:28:58.780
surrounded by young girls

00:28:58.780 --> 00:29:00.380
who'd see you as the ideal partner.

00:29:01.660 --> 00:29:03.700
Even if you say you won't get restless,

00:29:04.620 --> 00:29:05.820
I won't believe you.

00:29:06.020 --> 00:29:07.700
A man who's set on betraying you

00:29:07.700 --> 00:29:09.220
doesn't need to wait till you're older,

00:29:09.380 --> 00:29:11.220
nor does he need some gorgeous girl.

00:29:11.780 --> 00:29:13.420
Of course, you can doubt me.

00:29:13.420 --> 00:29:14.460
But what I'm saying is...

00:29:14.780 --> 00:29:16.180
if you're willing to take a gamble,

00:29:16.900 --> 00:29:18.420
why not go for what you truly want?

00:29:25.300 --> 00:29:26.140
Alright.

00:29:26.420 --> 00:29:27.540
So you're saying yes?

00:29:28.660 --> 00:29:29.500
No.

00:29:31.860 --> 00:29:32.980
Just...

00:29:33.380 --> 00:29:34.420
playing hard to get.

00:29:35.100 --> 00:29:37.220
Or maybe I want to be your Sis a bit longer.

00:29:37.980 --> 00:29:39.780
Give me some time to think it through.

00:29:40.300 --> 00:29:41.340
How much longer though?

00:29:41.620 --> 00:29:43.700
At least ten days, maybe two weeks.

00:29:44.060 --> 00:29:44.980
That long?

00:29:44.980 --> 00:29:46.740
Wait for my word, kiddo.

00:29:49.540 --> 00:29:50.380
Alright.

00:29:51.140 --> 00:29:52.180
Let's start over.

00:30:25.740 --> 00:30:26.620
Mingming.

00:30:30.140 --> 00:30:31.660
Why are you back so late?

00:30:32.020 --> 00:30:33.300
I was nearly eaten alive.

00:30:33.540 --> 00:30:34.420
Didn't you go to…

00:30:34.420 --> 00:30:35.460
your friend's place?

00:30:35.460 --> 00:30:36.300
Mm.

00:30:36.940 --> 00:30:37.820
My boyfriend's.

00:30:48.300 --> 00:30:49.560
- Let's go.
- Yeah.

00:30:50.620 --> 00:30:51.980
Come on, get inside quick.

00:30:58.300 --> 00:30:59.620
I didn't expect you to show up.

00:30:59.620 --> 00:31:00.660
Really, it's so sudden.

00:31:02.420 --> 00:31:03.740
The place is a bit messy.

00:31:03.740 --> 00:31:04.820
Please don't mind it.

00:31:05.900 --> 00:31:07.700
You should've given me a heads-up first.

00:31:07.940 --> 00:31:08.860
It's fine, really.

00:31:09.180 --> 00:31:10.500
But if I told you in advance,

00:31:10.500 --> 00:31:11.860
how'd it still be a surprise?

00:31:12.300 --> 00:31:13.380
If you call this a surprise…

00:31:13.380 --> 00:31:14.220
Of course it is.

00:31:15.780 --> 00:31:16.740
You know what?

00:31:17.260 --> 00:31:18.700
When you texted me earlier,

00:31:18.700 --> 00:31:19.780
saying you weren't coming,

00:31:19.780 --> 00:31:20.780
I actually thought you…

00:31:20.780 --> 00:31:22.260
regretted…

00:31:22.260 --> 00:31:24.020
regretted being my girlfriend.

00:31:24.620 --> 00:31:25.620
Are you that insecure?

00:31:28.420 --> 00:31:30.020
I know not showing up tonight

00:31:30.260 --> 00:31:31.540
made things awkward for you.

00:31:32.020 --> 00:31:33.100
But

00:31:33.780 --> 00:31:35.460
I just wanted some quiet time.

00:31:36.140 --> 00:31:37.460
Just the two of us.

