Jiang Yifan.

00:39:24.980 --> 00:39:26.780
There's something that might piss you off,

00:39:27.460 --> 00:39:28.620
but I'm gonna say it anyway.

00:39:30.860 --> 00:39:31.940
I miss you a lot.

00:39:33.620 --> 00:39:34.700
What are you talking about?

00:39:34.820 --> 00:39:36.420
I love you so much.

00:39:38.220 --> 00:39:40.100
So much that I don't even wanna be with you.

