00:40:47.660 --> 00:40:50.220
filled instead with hidden greed and desire.

00:40:52.460 --> 00:40:53.780
With every piece he placed,

00:40:53.780 --> 00:40:55.500
his fear and unfamiliarity toward her

00:40:55.500 --> 00:40:56.700
only deepened.

00:41:01.620 --> 00:41:02.660
Are you worried Jiang Yifan

00:41:02.660 --> 00:41:04.140
might turn into someone you hate?

00:41:07.300 --> 00:41:08.540
I'm scared you'll stop

00:41:10.060 --> 00:41:11.340
being you because of me.

00:41:13.820 --> 00:41:14.940
I gave up on the puzzle,

00:41:14.940 --> 00:41:16.370
on building the ideal version of you,

00:41:17.220 --> 00:41:18.260
