00:41:26.100 --> 00:41:28.060
You've given me the best of Jiang Yifan.

00:41:28.700 --> 00:41:29.540
That's enough.

00:41:30.780 --> 00:41:33.460
As for Li Xiaoxi,

00:41:33.900 --> 00:41:34.820
let's just say...

00:41:35.500 --> 00:41:36.740
I don't care about other women.

00:41:37.100 --> 00:41:38.100
All I know is,

00:41:40.700 --> 00:41:42.100
